	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I suggested 16 cycles because as I understand it, the longest CPU instruction takes 11 cycles (7-cycle instruction + 4-cycle DPCM DMA).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


