	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />tepples' "rough estimate" suggestion also has the advantage of leaving the cycle-critical stuff to the cycle-by-cycle emulation code, rather than to the prediction code. All the precise stuff is handled as it comes, rather than having to perfectly predict it in advance.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


